CRANE CO., a Corporation, Appellant, v. MERCO NORDSTROM VALVE CO., Appellee. No. 7993. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Dec. 20, 1935. Miller & Boyken, of San Francisco, Cal., and Ira J. Wilson, of Chicago, Ill., for appellant. Lyon & Lyon, of Los Angeles, Cal., and Wm. A. Strauch, of Washington, D. C., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, MATHEWS, and HANEY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of appellant, ordered appeal dismissed, that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and the mandate of this court be issued forthwith.
